bioghist.head: Historical Note
bioghist.p: Teamsters Local 116 served members in Fargo, North Dakota and neighboring Moorhead, Minnesota.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Please cite unpublished materials in the following way: Please provide the title and date of item, catalog number (if applicable it will be found written on the folder), name of the collection, name of the repository, and location of the repository. Example: James Oglethorpe to the Trustees, 13 January 1876, RG0001 Series 1, Box 4, Folder 3. Records of the Board of Trustees, Special Collections Research Center, Gelman Library, The George Washington University, Washington, D.C.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The collection contains two series; company files and general files. The latter includes material from Teamster-affiliated organizations outside of Local 116.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This series contains company files related to Teamsters Local 116 and other locals dating from 1941-2007. The files are mainly comprised of local union collective bargaining agreements and contract negotiation but also include correspondence, reports, handbooks and other miscellaneous material.
